1248
01:53:51,742 --> 01:53:53,703
<i>Now I can finally admit.</i>

1249
01:53:54,829 --> 01:53:59,208
<i>All the months in isolation,
yearning to be back in the marsh,</i>

1250
01:53:59,875 --> 01:54:02,712
<i>it was knowing
how much was left to explore,</i>

1251
01:54:03,671 --> 01:54:06,132
<i>how much life to uncover in the wild,</i>

1252
01:54:06,215 --> 01:54:07,383
<i>that kept me going.</i>

1253
01:54:09,635 --> 01:54:10,886
<i>And the hope,</i>

1254
01:54:11,721 --> 01:54:13,097
<i>always that hope...</i>

1255
01:54:14,682 --> 01:54:16,642
<i>that one day I could share it...</i>

1256
01:54:19,020 --> 01:54:21,856
<i>with the only person
I had ever truly loved.</i>

1257
01:54:52,511 --> 01:54:53,596
Kya!

1258
01:54:55,139 --> 01:54:56,139
Kya.

1259
01:55:11,947 --> 01:55:12,947
Hey.

1260
01:55:13,657 --> 01:55:15,034
You know I love you, right?

1261
01:56:19,723 --> 01:56:20,723
What?

1262
01:56:21,433 --> 01:56:24,270
